<h3 id="dijkstra-算法-知乎" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#dijkstra-算法-知乎" aria-hidden="true">#</a> <a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/338414118" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Dijkstra 算法 - 知乎<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></h3>
<h3 id="交换两不同值变量的值" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#交换两不同值变量的值" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 交换两不同值变量的值</h3>
<p>仅限不同值的交换，若值相同则直接成 0</p>
<div class="language-java ext-java line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code>a <span class="token operator">=</span> a <span class="token operator">^</span> b<span class="token punctuation">;</span>	<span class="token comment">// a1 = a0 ^ b0</span>
b <span class="token operator">=</span> a <span class="token operator">^</span> b<span class="token punctuation">;</span>	<span class="token comment">// b1 = a1 ^ b0 = a0 ^ b0 ^ b0 = a0</span>
